<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Application_Resource_View directly instantiates Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ViewRenderer rather than using the helper broker so the options passed in through Zend_Application aren't actually kept. To fix this, it should be as simple as changing:</p>

<p>Zend/Application/Resource/View.php</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $viewRenderer = new Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ViewRenderer();
</code></pre>

<p>to:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
        $viewRenderer = Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getStaticHelper('viewRenderer');
</code></pre>

    </div>
</div>

